Team


Decades of investing experience













Led by 36 Managing Directors across the United States, Europe, Asia and Australia, Bain Capital Credit’s culture is team-oriented and performance driven.  Our collaborative environment has resulted in low employee turnover, creating a team that has invested together through multiple market cycles.  Our team of over 110 investment professionals is assisted by a robust team of over 120 highly-tenured analysts, financial experts and other support staff.  Importantly, our Europe, Asia and Australia offices are staffed with natives of each region, who provide differential insight into sourcing channels and legal regimes.
 






 

